388
00:16:59,687 --> 00:17:00,897
HUNTER:
Me encontre um irmão diferente.

389
00:17:00,980 --> 00:17:02,815
MILES:
Talvez eu possa ser um.

390
00:17:05,652 --> 00:17:08,696
