396
00:17:31,344 --> 00:17:33,972
JENNA:
Oh... onde está o barco?

397
00:17:34,055 --> 00:17:35,098
DALLAS:
Deve chegar a qualquer minuto!

398
00:17:35,181 --> 00:17:39,185
